<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l28">mit <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> brief / Als der hochwirdıg fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l29">Johans Byſchof cʒü <expan>VVircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Eberhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l30"><expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der ker <expan>gebrüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan> von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> kere / allen iren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_350_r2l31"><expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>aufgedrukte<ex>n</ex></expan> Jnſigel </ab>
